  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para> 
<list>
<item>Describe the physical processes necessary to produce laser light</item>
<item>Explain the difference between coherent and incoherent light</item>
<item>Describe the application of lasers to a CD and Blu-Ray player</item>
</list></md:abstract>
